data.description: Discover the epitome of townhouse living in this 3-bed, 2.5-bath end unit condo. Nestled in tranquility, the screened back porch provides a private retreat overlooking a lush wooded conservation area. The first level boasts a seamlessly open kitchen, living room, dining space, a convenient half bath, and porch – an ideal setting for relaxation. Ascend to the second floor to find the of comfort with 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, and a conveniently located laundry room. The master suite is a true sanctuary, featuring a generously sized closet and a master bath adorned with 2 sinks, a separate tub and shower, offering a touch of luxury to your daily routine. The condo comes with a 1 car garage and a driveway for a 2nd car. Plenty of storage with large closest on the porch and storage under the steps. Ideal location only 10-minute drive to Amelia Island's pristine beaches, shopping and restaurants.
